@xx_qwertyuiop_xx wrote:

Ok, calm down.

First, for every left bracket, there must be a right.
The first mistake you have made is not putting a closing bracket on your if statement.
Second, you have forgotten to put a closing brace on your third if statement.
Third, you have not put an opening bracket on your call of deleteItem.
